      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Pavement is of cream colored tesserae with an inscribed medallion of five rows of tessarae colored (from the inside out) black, red, orange, cream, and black. Dimension given is the medallion's diameter. Diagonal rows of multicolored tesserae decorate the corners. Inscription is made of black and red tesserae.</p>
         </div>
